longBusinessSummary: Tiande Chemical Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research, development, manufacture, and sale of fine chemical products in the People's Republic of China, India, the United States, Singapore, Spain, and internationally. Its principal products include cyanoacetates, malonates, sodium cyanide, cyanoacetic acid, ethanol, tert-butanol, chloroacetic acid, cyanuric chloride, sodium methoxide, cyclohexyldiacetic acid, cyclohexyl diacetic acid monoamide, dihydroxypyrimidine, and EDTA acids. The company engages in research and development, manufacture, and sale of adhesive products. Tiande Chemical Holdings Limited was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Weifang, the People's Republic of China. The company operates as a subsidiary of Cheerhill Group Limited.
